### Manifestar interesse (buyer)
POST http://localhost:8080/interests
Authorization: Bearer {{token_buyer}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "listingId": "{{listing_id}}",
  "message": "Ola, o livro ainda esta disponivel? Consigo retirar na Vila Madalena."
}

### Listar minhas conversas (buyer)
GET http://localhost:8080/interests/threads?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token_buyer}}

### Ver mensagens de uma thread
GET http://localhost:8080/interests/threads/{{thread_id}}/messages?page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token_buyer}}

### Seller responde
POST http://localhost:8080/interests/threads/{{thread_id}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token_seller}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Sim, esta disponivel. Posso encontrar na estacao Vila Madalena amanha as 18h."
}

### Contagem de nao lidas (seller deve ter 1 nao lida agora)
GET http://localhost:8080/interests/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token_seller}}

### Ler mensagens (seller) — marca como lida
GET http://localhost:8080/interests/threads/{{thread_id}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token_seller}}

### Contagem agora deve ser 0
GET http://localhost:8080/interests/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token_seller}}

### Tentar interesse no proprio listing (esperar 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/interests
Authorization: Bearer {{token_seller}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "listingId": "{{own_listing_id}}",
  "message": "teste"
}

### Tentar mensagem em thread alheia (esperar 403)
POST http://localhost:8080/interests/threads/{{thread_id}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token_outro_user}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "intruso"
}
